   "fieldtype": "Select",
   "label": "Loss Category",
   "options": "\nPrice\nTechnical Non-Compliance\nDelivery Schedule\nVendor Approval / Eligibility\nCommercial Terms\nDocumentation\nCustomer Preference\nCompetitor Relationship\nPurchase Preference / Policy\nTender Cancelled\nNo Bid / Withdrawn\nOther"
  },
  {
