   "options": "\nL1 / Lowest Evaluated Price\nBuyer Selected\nTechnical Strength\nExisting Vendor Approval\nDelivery Capability\nQuality Performance\nPast Performance\nCustomer Relationship\nCommercial Terms\nMSE / MII Purchase Preference\nSingle Qualified Bidder\nOther",
